header.summary: Determined Developer lends more than 4 years of expertise in developing web-planning projects in fast-paced environments requiring fast turnaround. Blends detailed knowledge of programming aspects with interpersonal, communicative nature. Thorough grasp of front-end and back-end contributes to generating custom script for specific organizational needs.

projects.description: Vue blogs is created with Vue.js and Nodejs. User Can create, read and comment on blogs.
projects.title: Vue Blogs

projects.description: This simple app is built with Vue.js and REST COUNTRIES to get countries data. In this application user can filter countries in any continent or by name.
projects.title: Rest Countries

projects.description: Weather app is built with Vue.js and I used Open Weather Api to get weather data. You can search weather of any city in the world.
projects.title: Vue Weather

projects.description: This simple game is built with Vanilla HTML, CSS and JavaScript. User have to guess the RGB color in the background in the given time.
projects.title: Guess The Color

projects.description: Tic Tac Toe is built with HTML, CSS and JavaScript
projects.title: Tic Tac Toe

projects.description: This multiplayer quiz application is built with Unity 3d game engine and Firebase realtime database. User can take quiz on any category or can challenge his friend to play with him.
projects.title: Quiz Of Intelligence

contact.description: I'll be more than happy to answer any query so please feel free to ask anything.
